content.p: We offer focused programmes that provide the opportunity for you to explore specific topics in depth. These programmes are designed for individuals at all levels - from mid to top-level executives and general managers to up-and-coming leaders and business owners. Each programme aims to prepare the individuals for greater responsibilities and progression in their companies. Information on programmes available in 2022 will be available soon. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8000 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8019
